    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.58 + tmp + 0.99) * v2) - wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.96)))
    v0 = (tmp + ((v0 + 0.04 - tmp + 0.81) + wp.cos(v1 + 1.0)))
    v1 = tmp
